# Force LF line endings in the working tree on every platform.
# Prettier (no `endOfLine` override in prettier.config.js) defaults to enforcing
# LF, but Windows checkouts under `core.autocrlf=true` were producing CRLF and
# tripping `format:check` on every fresh worktree. With this file, Git stores
# and checks out LF for all text content regardless of platform / autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Lockfiles and snapshots — keep verbatim.
bun.lock binary
*.snap binary

# Binary asset types — never line-end-normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
